341
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:00,560
It was the Ge family

342
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:02,160
who brought them a bowl of rice soup

343
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,420
and saved their lives.

344
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:05,640
Later,

345
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:08,320
the Chen family

346
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,720
settled down here.

347
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:10,960
One year,

348
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,440
