349
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:14,440
and the Ge family's house

350
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,730
was destroyed by the flood.

351
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,920
It was the Chen family

352
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:22,160
who helped the Ge family

353
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:24,920
rebuild their house.

354
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:26,480
A few years later,

355
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,440
