356
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:33,000
and the Chen family's house

357
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,760
was blown down by the typhoon.

358
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:37,320
It was the Ge family

359
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:40,120
who helped them rebuild their house again.

360
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,400
And then?

361
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:44,200
Grandpa,

362
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,480
