363
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,520
I'm so dizzy.

364
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,880
And then,

365
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:57,680
it became what you see today.

366
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,200
Everyone is together,

367
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,600
and happy.

368
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:05,880
