377
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,520
Have a taste.

378
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,320
Chao! Chao!

379
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:32,400
Come to my house for dinner, Chao.

380
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:36,480
Chao,

381
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,440
