382
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:39,240
My mom made coconut milk chicken.

383
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,000
Okay.

384
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:40,640
Let's go.

385
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,320
Mom.

386
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:46,400
Chao is here.

387
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,080
Great.

388
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:49,080
