389
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:49,920
Hello, Auntie.

390
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:50,960
Hello. Come and sit.

391
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,020
Dad. Hello, Uncle.

392
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:54,300
