397
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:00,840
Eat up.

398
00:19:00,840 --> 00:19:01,320
Eat up.

399
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:43,600
Quick.

400
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:44,480
Hurry up,

401
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,400
