409
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:10,920
When I first came,

410
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,680
I saw how harmonious everyone was,

411
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:14,010
and I was quite envious.

412
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:17,010
