415
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:23,330
but you're actually laughing.

416
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,410
You misunderstood.

417
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,210
This is a happy funeral.

418
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,610
What do you mean?

419
00:21:34,120 --> 00:21:35,600
Grandpa was 75 years old.

420
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:37,840
Although his health wasn't particularly good,

421
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:39,360
and he wasn't considered very old,

422
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:41,000
he had both virtue and longevity,

423
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,260
