424
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:45,120
and he passed away in his sleep

425
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:46,280
without illness or pain.

426
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,680
He was a blessed person.

427
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:49,680
When such an elderly person in the family passes away,

428
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,840
