442
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,780
You could say that.

443
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:31,140
Being able to clearly arrange one's own affairs

444
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:33,600
is indeed a fortunate thing.

445
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,320
Grandpa's photo.

446
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:41,320
