472
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,600
If it rains,

473
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:58,020
just let it rain on you for a while.

474
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:01,080
How does the saying go?

475
00:24:03,280 --> 00:24:05,840
Every obstacle is hard, but you overcome every one.

476
00:24:05,840 --> 00:24:08,560
Every step is hard, but you take every step.

477
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:12,160
When you encounter a hurdle,

478
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,160
just step over it.

479
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:14,600
It's no big deal.

480
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:16,520
If you get lost,

481
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:17,880
don't be nervous.

482
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,650
Just keep walking and looking.

483
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:20,960
At worst,

484
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,490
Taking a little detour.

485
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:23,640
As long as you

486
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:26,360
keep moving forward

487
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:28,530
and don't look back,

488
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:31,760
then you will definitely

489
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,040
see the sun.

490
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:39,250
Understood.

491
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:50,720
Although physical death will destroy a person,

492
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,320
