493
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:53,680
can save them.

494
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:56,960
And those spirits and virtues

495
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,920
will also save those left behind.

496
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:03,280
Loved ones won't turn into stars,

497
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:05,000
but their light

498
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:07,200
will stay in our hearts forever.

499
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:44,960
Difficult times,

500
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,520
are hard to pass.

501
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:48,880
But they

502
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,240
will pass.

503
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:55,640
It's hard.

504
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,000
Keep walking,

505
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,680
step by step.

506
00:26:02,360 --> 00:26:03,400
Have a candy.

507
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,240
Have a candy.

508
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,240
Are you ready?

509
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,160
Let's go.

510
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,200
Thank you.

511
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,640
Here.

512
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:55,720
Take this to eat on the road.

513
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:58,000
These are for you and Xiaochao to take back.

514
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,530
Take good care of Xiaorong.

515
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:01,980
We'll be back for the New Year.

516
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,200
Xiaorong,

517
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,320
