520
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:12,120
Come back and visit often.

521
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:15,400
Come back often.

522
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,640
I'll miss you all.

523
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,000
We will.

524
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:22,980
We're leaving now.

525
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:23,720
Go.

526
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,640
Safe travels.

527
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,600
Bye-bye.

528
00:27:26,600 --> 00:27:27,880
Have a safe trip.

529
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,360
Drive safely.

530
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:31,880
Drive safely.

531
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,000
Let us know when you arrive.

532
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:33,800
Okay.

533
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,960
Xiaorong, be safe.

534
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,440
Okay.

535
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,160
Bye-bye.

536
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:39,360
Okay.

537
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:39,920
Goodbye.

538
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:40,680
