589
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:38,120
I was just

590
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,360
thinking about Grandpa.

591
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,560
He could even face death.

592
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,620
I shouldn't run away anymore.

593
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,920
Drink some water.

594
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:52,840
I'm leaving.

595
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:53,400
Okay.

596
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,320
Chen Rong.

597
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:16,840
He Chuan.

598
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:19,040
I just went to the office to look for you.

599
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,400
Wait a moment.

600
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:22,260
Zhang Chao.

601
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:24,570
Take the local products back with you.

602
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,480
Don't forget what you said in the car.

603
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,480
I'll wait for you.

604
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:28,720
See you tomorrow.

605
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,720
See you tomorrow.

606
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,720
Why did grandpa suddenly...

607
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,000
I should have gone back with you.

608
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,840
It's fine.

609
00:31:39,280 --> 00:31:40,720
Grandpa had a happy funeral.

610
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,250
Everything went smoothly.

611
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:43,720
But,

612
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:45,600
why are you with Zhang Chao?

613
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:48,360
Did you go back to Gechen Village together?

614
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:51,800
I'm in a hurry.

615
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:53,320
Let's talk later.

616
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:10,040
Girls!

617
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:13,000
Cheers!

618
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:14,120
Cheers!

619
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:15,120
Over here!

620
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:16,760
Bottoms up!

621
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,880
Xiaoyu, is that a new watch?

622
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,810
It looks so good!

623
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:36,800
Sir.

624
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:37,600
What's wrong?

625
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:38,800
Miss, excuse me.

626
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,000
The room is over here.

627
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,980
It's limited edition.

628
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,080
Limited edition.

629
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:05,000
Let me tell you.

630
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,760
Xiaoyu.

631
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:06,920
Is that your friend,

632
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:07,880
Bai Qiu?

633
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:11,320
Hello, dear!

634
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:13,640
Let me introduce to you,

635
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,560
my good friend,

636
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:15,120
Bai Qiu.

637
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:16,160
Come on.

638
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:17,920
Hello.

639
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:20,920
I'll introduce a new friend to you today,

640
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:21,600
Yueyue.

641
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:22,720
Yueyue.

642
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:24,280
Say hi.

643
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:28,960
Fang Yue,

644
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,400
our beautiful sales rep.

645
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,920
What do you think?

646
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,000
Isn't she pretty?

647
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,440
Which of your friends isn't?

648
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,720
I'm Bai Qiu.

649
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,720
Nice to meet you.

650
00:33:38,080 --> 00:33:39,560
Hello, I'm Fang Yue.

651
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:40,800
Just call me Yueyue.

652
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,440
Come on.

653
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:47,760
Please take care of me.

654
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:53,800
Don't just stand there awkwardly.

655
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,800
Sit down and talk.

656
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:56,530
Sit down and take your time.

657
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:02,760
Did you notice

658
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:03,880
who she looks like?

659
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,080
Who?

660
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,610
Now that you mention it,

661
00:34:12,679 --> 00:34:14,340
I actually remember someone.

662
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,440
Who?

663
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,280
It seems to be

664
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,300
an actress from Hong Kong.

665
00:34:27,199 --> 00:34:28,130
What's her name?

666
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:30,040
You flatter me too much.

667
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:31,440
Yueyue.

668
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,520
Amy,

669
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:39,020
give me your phone.

670
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:43,719
I mean Shasha.

671
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:46,360
Shasha?

672
00:34:47,239 --> 00:34:48,040
Who is Shasha?

673
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,580
A good friend of yours.

674
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,639
You must have mistaken me for someone else.

675
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:55,679
I don't remember having a friend named Shasha.

676
00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:57,560
But I've seen your pictures

677
00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:58,960
on her Moments.

678
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:13,160
Love, Qiu.

679
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:17,520
Probably the same name.

680
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,400
My first name is just Qiu,

681
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,360
so it's not that special.

682
00:35:24,720 --> 00:35:27,920
I think you're just forgetful, Miss Bai.

683
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:30,690
You have too many friends to remember.

684
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:33,240
Whether you have this friend or not,

685
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,540
just check your phone,

686
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,240
and you'll know.

687
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:44,440
Xiaochao, tell me.

688
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,640
Weihao...

689
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:47,480
Did he tell you anything?

690
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:49,600
You are good friends with him.

691
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,240
Did he tell you anything?

692
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,960
Does he hate me?

693
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:56,040
Tell me.

694
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,560
Let go. Let go. Let go.
